# Frontend Analytics — Deep Analysis
> **Repo:** `mastergroup-analytics-dashboard` (React + TypeScript + Vite)  
> **Deployed:** Netlify (`master-dashboard.netlify.app`) + PM2 on EC2 (port 3000)  
> **API base:** `VITE_API_BASE_URL=/api/v1` (Netlify proxy) or `http://localhost:8001/api/v1` (local)

---

## 1. App Architecture

```
index.tsx
  └── App.tsx (React Router)
       ├── /login → LoginScreen.tsx (JWT auth, stores token in localStorage)
       └── / → ProtectedRoute → Wireframe.tsx  (the entire dashboard)
                ├── aside (left sidebar) → RevenueTrendSection (navigation!)
                └── main
                     ├── DashboardHeaderSection  (top bar)
                     ├── Global Filter Bar       (time, category, source, delivered)
                     └── Active View (8 views)
```

### View Router (inside Wireframe.tsx)
| `activeView` State | Component Rendered |
|--------------------|-------------------|
| [Dashboard](file:///Users/clustox_1/Documents/MasterGroup-RecommendationSystem/mastergroup-analytics-dashboard/src/services/api.ts#59-68) (default) | PerformanceMetrics + TopProducts + POSvsOE + OrderStatus + RecentActivity |
| `Customer Profiling` | CustomerDetailedProfiling |
| `Cross-Selling` | CrossSellingSection |
| `Collaborative Filtering` | CollaborativeRecommendationDashboard |
| `Geographic Intelligence` | GeographicIntelligenceSection |
| `RFM Segmentation` | RFMSegmentationSection |
| `ML Recommendations` | AWSPersonalizeSection |

> Navigation is done by the **left sidebar** (`RevenueTrendSection`) calling `onNavigate(setActiveView)` — it's both a sidebar nav and a revenue chart.

---

## 2. Global Filter System

All filters live in [Wireframe.tsx](file:///Users/clustox_1/Documents/MasterGroup-RecommendationSystem/mastergroup-analytics-dashboard/src/screens/Wireframe/Wireframe.tsx) and are passed down as props to every section.

| Filter | State | Options |
|--------|-------|---------|
| **Time Period** | `timeFilter` (default: `'7days'`) | Today, 7d, 30d, MTD, 3M, 6M, 1Y, 2Y, 3Y, Custom Range, All |
| **Categories** | `selectedCategories[]` | MultiSelect (up to 20 from `/analytics/product-categories`) |
| **Order Source** | `orderSource` (default: `'all'`) | All / OE (Online Express) / POS (Point of Sale) |
| **Delivered Only** | `deliveredOnly` (default: `false`) | Checkbox — filters to Delivered+Completed only |
| **Custom Date** | `customStartDate:customEndDate` | triggers `time_filter=2025-01-01:2025-12-31` format |

### Smart Filter Visibility (per screen)

| Screen | Time? | Category? | Source? | Delivered? |
|--------|-------|-----------|---------|------------|
| Dashboard | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |
| Customer Profiling | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ |
| Cross-Selling | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ |
| Collaborative Filtering | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ |
| Geographic Intelligence | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ |
| RFM Segmentation | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ |
| ML Recommendations | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ |

> Active filters shown as colored **removable badge pills** (blue=source, green=delivered, purple=categories)

