## 5. Custom Hooks

| Hook | Used By | What it does |
|------|---------|-------------|
| `useDashboardMetrics` | PerformanceMetrics | Fetches KPI metrics, handles auto-refresh, engine online check |
| `useCollaborativeMetrics` | Collaborative | Fetches CF-specific metrics, loading/error state |
| `useMLRecommendations` | RFM, AWSPersonalize | Gets ML status + triggers training + loads recommendations per user |
| `useProducts` | TopProducts | Fetches popular products with pagination |

---

## 6. Shared UI Components

| Component | Purpose |
|-----------|---------|
| `DateRangeDisplay` | Shows human-readable date range + record count badge |
| `ExplanationCard` | Collapsible info card explaining each algorithm's methodology |
| `MultiSelectFilter` | Checkbox dropdown for multi-category filter |
| `DashboardExportButton` | Context-aware CSV export button (passes timeFilter + categories + sections) |
| `ExportButton` / `ScreenExportButton` | Per-section download to CSV |
| `MLStatusDashboard` | ML training status panel with 4 algorithm badges |
| `Tooltip` / `GeographicScoreTooltip` / `RFMScoreTooltip` | Info popovers |

---

## 7. Notable Design Patterns

> [!NOTE]
> **No charting library used** — all visualizations are built with raw CSS (`height: X%`, gradient bars, flex layout). No Recharts, Chart.js, or D3. Bars and progress charts are plain `div` elements with inline `style={{width: X%}}`.

> [!NOTE]
> **Fallback strategy** — [getCollaborativeMetrics()](file:///Users/clustox_1/Documents/MasterGroup-RecommendationSystem/mastergroup-analytics-dashboard/src/services/api.ts#486-516) catches all errors and returns hardcoded mock data (`total_recommendations: 15847, avg_similarity_score: 0.78`). This means that screen always shows data even if the backend endpoint is unimplemented.

> [!WARNING]
> **Hardcoded insight text** in [GeographicIntelligenceSection](file:///Users/clustox_1/Documents/MasterGroup-RecommendationSystem/mastergroup-analytics-dashboard/src/screens/Wireframe/sections/GeographicIntelligenceSection/GeographicIntelligenceSection.tsx#16-214) ExplanationCard: `"Punjab leads with 86K+ orders and PKR 4.8B revenue (93% of total)"` — this is static text, not calculated from live data. Live DB shows 201,471 orders for Punjab.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Auth:** JWT token stored in `localStorage` as `auth_token`. Every API call goes through [getAuthHeaders()](file:///Users/clustox_1/Documents/MasterGroup-RecommendationSystem/mastergroup-analytics-dashboard/src/services/api.ts#9-22). 401 responses auto-redirect to `/login` and clear the token.
